fluffyalien_asn.message.scriptEvent.addonRule.help.wirelessInterfaceRange=wirelessInterfaceRange: integer (default: 500) - The max range a wireless transmitter must be from a player for them to use a wireless interface. Set this to -1 to disable range and dimension checking.
