fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.title=Tutorial Book

fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageNetwork.title=Storage Network
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageNetwork.bullet0=A network of devices that can hold an infinite amount of items.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageNetwork.bullet1=Comprises one storage core and any number of storage drives and storage interfaces. Can also contain many other optional devices.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageNetwork.bullet2=Devices in the network must be placed next to each other or be connected with storage cables.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageNetwork.bullet3=To get started, you will need one storage core, one storage drive, and one storage interface or wireless storage interface. Read their respective tutorial entries for more information.

fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageCore.title=Storage Core
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageCore.bullet0=The core of a storage network.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageCore.bullet1=Required for a storage network to function.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageCore.bullet2=Only one of these blocks exists in a network.

fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageCable.title=Storage Cable
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageCable.bullet0=Connects devices in a storage network.

fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageDrive.title=Storage Drive
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageDrive.bullet0=Provides the network it's connected to with 3,000u of storage space.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageDrive.bullet1=Drops a storage disk when destroyed that contains the items the drive had before it was broken.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageDrive.bullet2=Any number of these devices can exist in a network.

fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageInterface.title=Storage Interface
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageInterface.bullet0=Allows players to add, remove, or view items in a storage network.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageInterface.bullet1=Any number of these devices can exist in a network.

fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.importBus.title=Storage Import Bus
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.importBus.bullet0=Imports items from the container it's facing into the storage network it's connected to.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.importBus.bullet1=Stops importing when receiving a redstone current.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.importBus.bullet2=Any number of these devices can exist in a network.

fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.exportBus.title=Storage Export Bus
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.exportBus.bullet0=Exports items from the storage network it's connected to into the container it's facing.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.exportBus.bullet1=More filter options are available when exporting an item that is enchantable or breakable.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.exportBus.bullet2=Stops exporting when receiving a redstone current.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.exportBus.bullet3=Interact with an empty hand to configure.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.exportBus.bullet4=Any number of these devices can exist in a network.

fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.levelEmitter.title=Storage Level Emitter
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.levelEmitter.bullet0=Tests that the total amount of a filtered set of item stacks in the storage network matches a query.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.levelEmitter.bullet1=Filter options are available when exporting an item that is enchantable or breakable.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.levelEmitter.bullet2=Activates the repeater in front of it when the test is true.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.levelEmitter.bullet3=Interact with an empty hand to configure.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.levelEmitter.bullet4=Any number of these devices can exist in a network.

fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.relay.title=Storage Relay
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.relay.bullet0=Connects storage network devices over long distances.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.relay.bullet1=Interact to change the relay name.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.relay.bullet2=Connects to all other relays with the same name.

fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.wirelessInterface.title=Wireless Storage Interface
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.wirelessInterface.bullet0=Allows players to add, remove, or view items in a storage network wirelessly.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.wirelessInterface.bullet1=Interact with a storage core while holding this item to link it to that network.

fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageDisk.title=Storage Disk
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageDisk.bullet0=A crafting item.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageDisk.bullet1=Can contain data.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.storageDisk.bullet2=Interact with an empty storage drive while holding a disk with data to deposit the items inside of the disk into the drive.

fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.addonRules.title=Add-On Configuration
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.addonRules.bullet0=Use the `/scriptevent fluffyalien_asn:addonrule <rule> [value]` command to change a rule.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.addonRules.bullet1=Use the `/scriptevent fluffyalien_asn:addonrule help` command for a list of rules.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.addonRules.bullet2=Omit `[value]` from the command to get the current value of the rule.

fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.energy.title=Energy (EXPERIMENTAL)
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.energy.bullet0=Energy usage can be enabled using the 'useEnergy' rule. See Add-On Configuration for more information.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.energy.bullet1=Energy is stored in Storage Power Bank blocks.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.energy.bullet2=Network energy consumption is scaled based on the amount of storage drives.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.energy.bullet3=Uses Bedrock Energistics Core energy. Requires the Bedrock Energistics Core add-on to be in the world.
fluffyalien_asn.ui.tutorialBook.entry.energy.bullet4=This add-on does not add any power generators, you must include another Bedrock Energistics Core powered add-on to generate energy for your system.